expanding economy and with an interest in promoting free
enterprise,'' said Heinz Chairman Anthony O'Reilly.
   Heinz withheld terms of the deal.
   Heinz and the government in neighboring Zimbabwe operate Olivine
Industries Ltd. a private producer in Harare of edible oils,
margarines and soaps.
